{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ditch the roles, hard counters and last hits in Sirocco, in a new MOBA inspired by the beloved Warcraft 3 mod: Battleships. Rally your team as you <strong>swap abilities</strong> mid-match, load up <strong>auto-firing weapons</strong>, and craft strategies on the fly. No rules \u2014 just fun.<br><br>Join the Discord and request access to Playtest Now!  <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/extras/WC3sirocco-ezgif.com-optimize__1_.gif?t=1739471746\" /><strong>Creativity As Meta </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Without fixed roles and hard counters, learn as you go and discover your own strategies instead of being punished for not following the strategies of others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/extras/loom_coil_steam.png?t=1739471746\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Auto-firing Arena, Not Farming Arena</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sirocco utilizes an auto-fire mechanic and economic system that promotes team fighting and positioning over last hitting NPCs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/extras/DopeReflect.gif?t=1739471746\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>High Risk, High Reward</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every Ability In Sirocco Is A Skill Shot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Deep Strategy, Not Memorization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine specialized weapons, ship abilities, and ability augmentations to develop your own way to play. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Conquer The Five Seas with your Friends by Making New Ones</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Sirocco, teams win, not individuals, so whether you are 10-0 or 0-10, our economic system ensures all your friends are critical to achieving victory.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739471746","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/page.bg.jpg?t=1739471746","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/f8124b3e503c6e4c8d78d0161b507f8a0aeb3770/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739471746","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/f8124b3e503c6e4c8d78d0161b507f8a0aeb3770/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739471746","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3488650,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ditch the roles, hard counters and last hits in Sirocco, in a new MOBA inspired by the beloved Warcraft 3 mod: Battleships. Rally your team as you <strong>swap abilities</strong> mid-match, load up <strong>auto-firing weapons</strong>, and craft strategies on the fly. No rules \u2014 just fun.<br><br>Join the Discord and request access to Playtest Now!  <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/extras/WC3sirocco-ezgif.com-optimize__1_.gif?t=1739471746\" /><strong>Creativity As Meta </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Without fixed roles and hard counters, learn as you go and discover your own strategies instead of being punished for not following the strategies of others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790090/extras/loom_coil_steam.png?t=1739471746\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Auto-firing Arena, Not Fa